Package com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.networks.nsx

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DistributedSwitches
    The DistributedSwitches interface provides methods to get the basic information of Distributed Switches.
    DistributedSwitches.ListInvocation
    Invocable that represents the DistributedSwitches#list vAPI operation.
    DistributedSwitchesTypes
    Defines the data types of the DistributedSwitches API service.
    Edges
    The Edges interface provides methods to retrieve the basic information for NSX Edges.
    Edges.ListInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Edges#list vAPI operation.
    EdgesTypes
    Defines the data types of the Edges API service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributedSwitchesDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the DistributedSwitches API service.

    Remote stub implementation of the DistributedSwitches API service.
    DistributedSwitchesTypes.FilterSpec
    The FilterSpec class contains properties used to filter the results when listing Distributed Switches (see DistributedSwitches.list()).
    DistributedSwitchesTypes.FilterSpec.Builder
    Builder class for DistributedSwitchesTypes.FilterSpec.
    DistributedSwitchesTypes.Summary
    The Summary class contains the basic information about a Distributed Switch.

    Builder class for DistributedSwitchesTypes.Summary.
    EdgesDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the Edges API service.
    EdgesStub
    Remote stub implementation of the Edges API service.
    EdgesTypes.FilterSpec
    The FilterSpec class contains properties used to filter the results when listing Edges (see Edges.list()).
    EdgesTypes.FilterSpec.Builder
    Builder class for EdgesTypes.FilterSpec.
    EdgesTypes.Summary
    The Summary class contains the basic information about an Edge.
    EdgesTypes.Summary.Builder
    Builder class for EdgesTypes.Summary.
    NsxFactory
    NsxFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.networks.nsx package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.networks.nsx package.
